title: Lancelot Link Secret Chimp (1970)
description:
In a world inhabited by chimps instead of humans, Lancelot Link and his partner Mata Hairi are top agents at the Agency to Prevent Evil (APE), a secret organization led by Commander Darwin that protects the world from wrongdoers.

APE's chief nemesis, Baron Von Butcher, leads the Criminal Headquarters for the Underworld Master Plan (CHUMP), an evil league bent on world conquest. Assisting the Baron is a band of bad apes including Creto, Wang Fu, The Duchess, Dragon Lady, Ali Assa Seen and Dr. Strangemind.

Episodes include musical segments featuring Lancelot Link and Mata Hairi's undercover band, The Evolution Revolution.
